	   <tr><td colspan=2>I agree Stonebrunt is a good place from probably mid 20's up through 40. <br><br>But I have a slightly different strategy than fearkiting. The biggest problem in the zone is with adds.&nbsp;&nbsp;If you fearkite a mob, he leads you where he wants to go, which is often into the path of one or more friends. I prefer to snare (ensnare when you get it) and pull him where YOU want to go. <br><br>That having been said, ALWAYS keep Panic Animal memmed. You still get a few adds even with my approach, and PA has saved my butt countless times by making the unsnared add run  away.  Often they will run out of aggro range, and you don't see them again, especialy if you pull your mob in the opposite direction from the add.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
