	   <tr><td colspan=2>How much you looking to spend is a good question.<br><br>Well lets see,<br><br>Arms:ulthork hide (8 ac 3 wis), normally vendor loot, you can kill ulthorks in EW for these for free or just cough up the 20pp at a vendor.<br><br>Rings: if you aren't major twinking, just get two Silver Jasper Rings for +2 wis each or two moonstone rings with 3 str 30 mana each(these are about 75pp a pair on my server)<br><br>Gloves: Nuff said, Splitpaw unless you want to spend a lot more money. for 5pp from a vendor or you can go loot them yourself you get a quick 2 wis bonus<br><br>Legs; Gatorscale Legs are about the only wis legs i see for sale under 500pp. If that doesn't work, look for mammoth hide leggings for about 25-50pp in your trading zone EC or Faymart<br><br>Head: Savants Cap, 3 wis and 2 ac for 25pp<br><br>Shoulder: Braided Ivy Cords for about 200pp for 5wis, or Lizard Scale for 3wis for about 100<br><br>Tunic: Foremans for about 100pp for 3 wis 3 str 13 ac, or brown chitin protector 12 ac 9/9/9 sta/dex/agi for about 150pp nowadays<br><br>Primary: Velium Etched Stone Mace for a few hundred pp for 3 wis 3 str.<br><br>Belt: Crystaline Belt for about 200pp for 3 wis and 3 agi and 10 hp belt.<br><br>Earrings: Two Golden Jasper Earrings for about 40pp each from a Jewelcrafting Player.<br><br>Face: Silver Ruby Viel for 100pp for 4 wis and str<br><br>Back: Spore Covered Cloak from Fungoids in Neth Lair is like 8 ac +1 wis, or you can get a kunzar cloak for 100pp which is like 7 ac 2 wis and some <br>mana i think.<br><br>Wrist: Two Polished Bone Bracers for 50pp each, 3 wis and 2 ac on them<br><br>Thats pretty much all i can think of unless you are wanting to spend large amounts of cash.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
