	   <tr><td colspan=2>I did this level at the north side of Nek Forest (time to payback the DEs for killing all the halflings).&nbsp;&nbsp;THere is one guard on the north side of the forest (at the LS Zone) that you should be able to do at this level.  He always drops a FS (or maybe bronze, has been a while) weapon that should sell well.  With camo and gate, you should be OK here, just stick to the West zone wall when running through.<br><br>Also you could try the Aviak guards in Lake Rath, near the Arena ent.  They sometimes drop plat and FS, but not very often for my liking.<br><br>I did the DE guard till about 21, then the Aviak Guards till about 24.  Got new spells and headed fro Everfrost... leveled to 30 in Everfrost.  Then i headed for HighKeep and leveled to 35 in the WR and RR there. <br><br>This is currently where i am at.  I am now traveling with some friends in my guild and we have bounced between several different places (GD, EW, IC, RM, MM, Perma to name a few) and i should be dinging tonight.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
