	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent<span id=notbold>[4.50]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Small spiders/spiderlings provide spiderling silks - 2 of these make a thread. Larger spiders (various breeds) provide spider silks - 2 of these make a swatch.<br><br>Threads are used to make bandages &amp; silk cords, as well as various other tailoring recipes. Swatches are used to make silk armour. Being completely different things (although I haven't done the quest you mention) probably means that swatches won't work. If the quest ask for threads, you'll need to get out there and slaughter more small spiders! (Even if they aren't giving you experience any more...)<br>&nbsp;<br>Kelanthor<br>Wood Elf Druid of the 41st Circle<br><a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212672" target=_new>http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=212672</a></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 >&nbsp;</td><td align=right valign=bottom>
	   <span style='font-weight: normal; font-size: 9px;'>[<a href=#top>Top</a>]</span></tr>
